{"title":"Splint mail","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Splint_mail","type":"markdown","data":"***Obsolete**: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.*\n\n| Name                                                           | Splint Mail   |\n| :------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------- |\n| Size to wear                                                   | Small, Medium |\n| [Armour Class](/Armour_class \"Armour class\")                   | 8             |\n| [Encumbrance rating](/Encumbrance_rating \"Encumbrance rating\") | -5            |\n| Maximum Enchantment                                            | +8            |\n| Grants                                                         | nothing       |\n| Time to Wear                                                   | 5             |\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |\n| - | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n|   | A heavy suit of body armour consisting of narrow strips of metal which are attached lengthwise to a thick leather backing. While offering great protection, splint mail is quite difficult to move in without proper training. |\n\n**Splint mail** is a fairly heavy suit of body [armour](/Armour \"Armour\"), providing defense similar to but worse than [plate armour](/Plate_armour \"Plate armour\"). Casters should never use it, and physical fighters should probably upgrade to something better when the opportunity arises. It does provide adequate protection for those who don't quite have the [strength](/Strength \"Strength\") to wear plate armour yet.\n\n|              | Image                                                                        |\n| ------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| **Mundane**  | [![Splint mail1.png](/images/e/ea/Splint_mail1.png)](/File:Splint_mail1.png) |\n| **Magical**  | [![Splint mail2.png](/images/f/f2/Splint_mail2.png)](/File:Splint_mail2.png) |\n| **Artifact** | [![Splint mail3.png](/images/e/e7/Splint_mail3.png)](/File:Splint_mail3.png) |\n\n## History\n\nSplint mail was removed in [0.13](/0.13 \"0.13\"), and chain mail was bumped up to 8 base AC to take its place.\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Splint mail - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Splint_mail\",\"wgTitle\":\"Splint mail\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":21813,\"wgRevisionId\":21813,\"wgArticleId\":2017,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Obsolete articles\",\"Body armour\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Splint_mail\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":2017,\"wgRequestId\":\"64869ed0843ffe23c