bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Obsolete</b>: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.</i></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; text-align:left\">\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Name\n</th>\n<td> Splint Mail\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Size to wear\n</th>\n<td> Small, Medium\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Armour_class\" title=\"Armour class\"> Armour Class</a>\n</th>\n<td> 8\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Encumbrance_rating\" title=\"Encumbrance rating\">Encumbrance rating</a>\n</th>\n<td> -5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Maximum Enchantment\n</th>\n<td> +8\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Grants\n</th>\n<td> nothing\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Time to Wear\n</th>\n<td> 5\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n</div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A heavy suit of body armour consisting of narrow strips of metal which are attached lengthwise to a thick leather backing. While offering great protection, splint mail is quite difficult to move in without proper training.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Splint mail</b> is a fairly heavy suit of body <a href=\"/Armour\" title=\"Armour\">armour</a>, providing defense similar to but worse than <a href=\"/Plate_armour\" title=\"Plate armour\">plate armour</a>. Casters should never use it, and physical fighters should probably upgrade to something better when the opportunity arises. It does provide adequate protection for those who don't quite have the <a href=\"/Strength\" title=\"Strength\">strength</a> to wear plate armour yet.\n</p>\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:auto; padding:0; text-align: center\">\n<tr>\n<th> </th>\n<th> Image\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td> <b>Mundane</b> </td>\n<td> <a href=\"/File:Splint_mail1.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Splint mail1.png\" src=\"/images/e/ea/Splint_mail1.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td> <b>Magical</b> </td>\n<td> <a href=\"/File:Splint_mail2.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Splint mail2.png\" src=\"/images/f/f2/Splint_mail2.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td> <b>Artifact</b> </td>\n<td> <a href=\"/File:Splint_mail3.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Splint mail3.png\" src=\"/images/e/e7/Splint_mail3.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<p>Splint mail was removed in <a href=\"/0.13\" title=\"0.13\">0.13</a>, and chain mail was bumped up to 8 base AC to take its place.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916130154\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.032 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.043 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 49/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 309/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1281/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 256/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 3/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   19.684      1 -total\n 85.56%   16.841      1 Template:Armour\n  6.61%    1.301      1 Template:Flavour\n  5.96%    1.173      1 Template:Obsolete\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:2017-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916130154 and revision id 21813\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\"